*Payne, Christopher, ed.. Sotheby&#x27;s Concise Encyclopedia of Furniture. London: Conran Octopus, 1989. As &quot;Vargueno&quot;: pp. 29, 30, 36, 67 ill. on pp. &quot;29, 36&quot;

