* &quot;Coalition: The Politics and Personalities of Coalition Government from 1850&quot;, Harriman House Publishing, 2007
* &quot;Screwing Up: How One MP Survived Politics, Scandal and Turning 40&quot;, Biteback Publishing Ltd, 2009

